quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  12,77,"Ba re: “Haeba u oa utsuoa, ho kile ha eba ngoana’bo pele ho ena ea neng a utsoa. Empa Josefa o ile a ipipetsa moeeng ka taba eo, a se ke a ba phetlela lekunutu. A ipolella hore: “Lona le maqakabetsing a ts’abehang, ‘Allah U tseba ka ho fetisisa ‘nete ea seo le se buang.”"
  12,78,"Ba re: “Oho mohlomphehi! Bona! Ntatae o se a holile haholo ebile o oa fokola, kahoo o ka mpa oa nka e mong oa rona sebakeng sa hae. Hobane Re eleletsoe hore u e mong oa ba etsang botle.”"
  12,79,"A re: “Ruri Allah U hana hore re ka ts’oara e mong sebakeng sa eo re fumaneng thepa ea rona ho eena; Ruri re tla be re le baetsa liphoso.”"
  12,80,"Ha ba se banyahame feela ho le boima ho mo lesa, ba ea thokoana ho ipuoa. Moholoane oa bona a re: “na ha le tsebe kamoo ntata lona a nkileng boikano ba lona Ka lebitso la Allah, le kamoo le kileng la sitoa ka ts’ebeletso ea Josefa linakong tse fetileng? Ka lebaka leo nke ke ka tsoa naheng ena ho fihlela ntate a ka ntumella, kapa Allah a ka ntaela joalo. Etsoe ke Eena ea molemo ka ho fetisisa har’a baahloli"
  12,81,"Khutlelang ho ntata lona le ‘molelle hore: “Oho ntata rona! Bona! mora’hau u utsoitsoe. Rona re mpa re fana ka bopaki feela ba seo re se tsebang; ha re balebeli ba tse sa bonoeng"
  12,82,"Tsamaea u botse motseng oo re neng re le ho ona, le bohle bao re neng re tsamaea le bona. Ruri re bua ‘nete.”"
  12,83,"Jakobo are: “Che, le mpa le lohile maqiti. ‹Na mosebetsi oa ka ka mehla ke mamello! Mohlomong Allah U tla ba khutlisetsa ho ‘na kaofela. Hobane ke Eena, Eena feela Setsibi sa Tsohle, ebile U Seli.”"
  12,84,"Jakobo a ba furalla a re: “Mesarelo ea ka e meholo ka Josefa!” Mahlo a hae a soeufala ke masisapelo a feheloa"
  12,85,"Ba re: “Ka Allah! Ha u sa tla tela ho hopola Josefa ho fihlela u kula, kapa ho fihlela u shoele!”"
  12,86,"Ke ha a re: “Ke mpa feela ke lebisa mesarelo le metouto ea ka ho Allah, ke na le tsebo ho tsoa ho Allah ea seo lona le sa se tsebeng"
  12,87,"Bara baka! Tsamaeang le ke le eo batlisisa hantle mabapi le Josefa le moena’e, le se lahleheloe ke ts’epo Mohaung oa Allah. Ruri! ha ho ea lahleheloang ke ts’epo Mohaung oa Allah, kantle ho ba senang tumelo.”"
  12,88,"Ha ba fihla ka pela Josefa, ba re: “Oho mohlomphehi! Re aparetsoe ke masoabi le lelapa la bo-rona, re tlisitse kananyetso e fokolang, kahoo re tlatsetse ka boima bo lekaneng, ebe joalo ka nyehelo ho rona. Hobane! Ruri Allah U putsa ba nyehelang.”"
  12,89,"A re: “Na le tseba seo le kileng la se etsa ka Josefa le moena’e, le sa tsebe?”"
  12,90,"Ba re: “Na Ruri ke uena Josefa?” A re: “Ke ‘na Josefa, enoa ke moena’ka. Ruri Allah U bile molemo ho rona. Bonang! Ea sesefang bobe a bile a ena le mamello o fumana molemo; hobane Ruri Allah a ke ke a lahla kherehloa moputso oa ba etsang tse ntle.”"
  12,91,"Ba re: “Ka Allah! Ruri Allah U u ratile ho feta rona, Ruri re molato oa sebe.”"
  12,92,"A re: “Se ts’abeng kajeno! Allah U tla le ts’oarela, etsoe ke Eena ea Khaphatsehang Mohau ka ho fetisisa har’a bohle ba bonts’ang mohau"
  12,93,"Tsamaeang le setipana sena sa ka, le fihle le kupetse sefahleho sa ntate ka sona, o tla boela a bona; joale e be le tla koano ho ‘na kaofela le lelapa la bo-lona.”"
  12,94,"Nakong eo khonatha e tlohang Egepeta ntata bona o ile a re: “Ruri ke nkhella bo-teng ba Josefa, le hoja lona le mpitsa ts’ere-ts’ere.”"
  12,95,"Ba re: “Ka Allah! Bona! Ruri u hlile u fokola kelellong ke botsofali.”"
  12,96,"Ha a fihla ka litaba tse molemo, a kupetsa ka setipana sefahlehong, hang a boela a bona. A re: “Ha ke’a ka kare ho lona, ke na le tsebo e tsoang ho Allah ea seo lona le sa se tsebeng?”"
  12,97,"Ba re: “Oho ntata rona! Re kopele ts’oarelo ea libe tsa rona, hobane! Ruri re bile sebeng.”"
  12,98,"A re: “Ke tla kopa Mong`a ka ho le ts’oarela. Hobane! Ruri U Ts’oarela-joalo-joalo, U Khaphatseha Mohau.”"
  12,99,"Ha ba fihla ho Josefa, o ile a ba amohela, a re: “Kenang Egepeta ka polokeho, haeba e le ka thato ea Allah!”"
  12,100,"O ile a phahamisetsa batsoali ba hae litulong tsa tlhompheho, kemoo bona ba oela fats’e kapel’a hae ba mo khumamela; empa a re: “Ntate! Sena ke manollo ea toro ea ka ea khale. Mong`a ka U entse hore e fetohe ‘nete, ebile U mponts’itse mosa nakong eo A neng A ntokolla chankaneng, A ba A le tlisa koano ho tsoa lehoatateng, kamor’a hoba Satane a fehle bora lipakeng tsa ka le bana beso. Ruri! Mong`a ka U na le kutloelo bohloko ho eo A ikhethelang eena. U Tseba Tsohle, U Hlokolosi.”"